{"tid":1380372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭出席青少年軍事夏令營結業禮　籲放遠目光留心國家發展","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T06:05:12.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec26466b911e9ae1c334d32eb0652d5a49437fd","tid":1380372,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190728/s00001/2a4fcf38f7841d0585b25515a1403d0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190728%2Fs00001%2F2a4fcf38f7841d0585b25515a1403d0a.jpg&h=3b0ad8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190728/s00001/2a4fdcf6f118c621e0aab51ce59570b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190728%2Fs00001%2F2a4fdcf6f118c621e0aab51ce59570b5.jpg&h=b60187a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今日（28日）出席2019香港青少年軍事夏令營結業典禮，出席者還包括全國政協副主席董建華、中聯辦主任王志民、解放軍駐港部隊司令員陳道祥等。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥致辭時表示，在「一國兩制」的獨特優勢下，香港正受惠於國家高速發展所帶來的種種機遇，寄語同學要將目光放遠，多留心國家各方面發展，並以開放態度接觸不同的人和事，積極為自己人生增值，未來為香港、國家和世界的發展，各盡所能，作出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又稱，青年人是香港發展的動力，特區政府會盡力支持青年的健康成長，又呼籲同學能將夏令營中的體會和學習成果帶回學校，與同學分享，讓未來有更多同學參與此一有意義活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190728/s00001/2a3def83d81910a2896236c5745362d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190728%2Fs00001%2F2a3def83d81910a2896236c5745362d5.jpg&h=5396f497&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50b30fe9266ac9c6c6431fb1cbb8c1fcef5526d6","tid":1380372,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ec26466b911e9ae1c334d32eb0652d5a49437fd","tid":1380372,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190728/s00001/2a4fcf38f7841d0585b25515a1403d0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190728%2Fs00001%2F2a4fcf38f7841d0585b25515a1403d0a.jpg&h=3b0ad8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190728/s00001/2a4fdcf6f118c621e0aab51ce59570b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190728%2Fs00001%2F2a4fdcf6f118c621e0aab51ce59570b5.jpg&h=b60187a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今日（28日）出席2019香港青少年軍事夏令營結業典禮，出席者還包括全國政協副主席董建華、中聯辦主任王志民、解放軍駐港部隊司令員陳道祥等。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥致辭時表示，在「一國兩制」的獨特優勢下，香港正受惠於國家高速發展所帶來的種種機遇，寄語同學要將目光放遠，多留心國家各方面發展，並以開放態度接觸不同的人和事，積極為自己人生增值，未來為香港、國家和世界的發展，各盡所能，作出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又稱，青年人是香港發展的動力，特區政府會盡力支持青年的健康成長，又呼籲同學能將夏令營中的體會和學習成果帶回學校，與同學分享，讓未來有更多同學參與此一有意義活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190728/s00001/2a3def83d81910a2896236c5745362d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190728%2Fs00001%2F2a3def83d81910a2896236c5745362d5.jpg&h=5396f497&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:08:33.000Z","msg":"學緊比美軍打爆之後點自盡？"},{"pid":"892d68087281880e98368596df27c6243b04e7b7","tid":1380372,"uid":68689,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"點解仲會有人參加軍事夏令營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdd704e96592c277be597a26e5a203d8d1183c8","tid":1380372,"uid":282438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:16:35.000Z","msg":"未來香港警察的新苗子"},{"pid":"436b924b122966d3fdf60e2af341c70f5dff2ec4","tid":1380372,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:17:03.000Z","msg":"個八婆仲笑得出"},{"pid":"dda28594169bd5c37b44ca4ff7123d4f0b3a964e","tid":1380372,"uid":11301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"明報想帶出咩信息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />張相有人打拳，之後後面寫住貫徹習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"